You will be in default of this Financing Program if any one of the following events (referred to as an “event of default”) occurs:
\na. You fail to make any payment required under this Financing Program within five (5) calendar days of the applicable due date;
\nb. You are in breach of any covenant, representation or warranty in this Financing Program;
\nc. You are in default in the performance of any other obligation in this Financing Program and such default continues for ten (10) calendar days after Robi provides you with notice of the default; or
\nd. You will not be allowed for MNP during the Financing Program period.
